description: This file is a C header file (.h) defining external API prototypes for the Npt Cmd Carrier component within the ANSC system. It includes license comments, module description, and function prototypes for creating command carrier and command objects.

methods.name: AnscCreateNptCmdCarrier
methods.description: Creates and initializes a new Npt Cmd Carrier object, returning a handle to it.

methods.name: AnscCreateNptCmd
methods.description: Creates and initializes a new Npt Cmd object of the specified type, returning a handle to it.
